Class Weapon

java.lang.Object
salable.Salable
salable.Weapon
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Weapon>
public class Weapon extends salable.Salable implements Comparable<Weapon>
The Weapon class represents a type of salable product which is a weapon. Weapons are derived specializations of Salable Products and are comparable based on their names.
